dev-issue-62.name: kevinrob/guzzle-cache-middleware
dev-issue-62.description: A HTTP/1.1 Cache for Guzzle 6. It's a simple Middleware to be added in the HandlerStack. (RFC 7234)

suggest.guzzlehttp/guzzle: For using this library. It was created for Guzzle6. (but you can use it with any PSR-7 HTTP Client)
suggest.doctrine/cache: This library have a lot of ready-to-use cache storage (to be use with Kevinrob\GuzzleCache\Storage\DoctrineCacheStorage)
